  "description": "<p><strong>Rugby Sevens Roving Crew </strong></p><p>Salary: $12phr</p><p>Location: National Stadium</p><p>Working Date and Time: </p><ul><li>31 January 2026 (10am - 8pm) x 12 pax</li><li>1 February 2026 (11am - 8pm) x 12 pax</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Min 18 years old and above (dealing with alcohol)</li><li>No long fingernails or manicure</li><li>No coloured hair</li><li>Tattoo to be covered up if there is any</li><li>30 mins to 1 hour unpaid break (timing and whether food is provided will be TBC)</li><li>Able to commit both days</li></ul><ul><li>Attire: Black plain polo shirt, black pants and covered shoe</li><li>(NO jeans/legging/tights/track pants/cargo pants/wide pleated pants or faded black pants)</li></ul><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Walk around the venue to promote and sell beer</li><li>Take beer orders and process payment using POS</li><li>Collect beer from the food stand and serve customers</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p>Log on to www.e-cruitteam.com.sg for more job opportunities!<br /><br />EA Personnel: Sia Kah Hui (Jia Hui)<br />EA Reg ID: R1980770<br />EA Licence No.:19C9603</p>",
